what they think about Putin's wealth. I'm not in a position to

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:02.989
give you figures, but what I can say is that he supposedly draws a state

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:08.989
salary of something like $110,000 a year. That is not an accurate

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:12.989
statement of the man's wealth. And he has long time training and

