practices in terms of how to mask his actual wealth. Is Vladimir Putin

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:25.989
corrupt? In our view, yes. How long has the United States known that

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:31.989
Vladimir Putin was, in your words, a corrupt figure? I think for many,

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:37.989
many years. Russia dismisses this sort of talk as nonsense. But the

