trail, and it's claimed Putin was at the heart of it. These are documents

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:23.989
from one of the offshore companies that diverted millions of dollars to

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:30.989
the palace. According to Kolesnikov, the owner of this company was Putin

