who've been linked to organised crime. They can be heard discussing

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:57.989
Putin's property in Spain. One of the gangsters says Putin's house is

00:12:58.000 --> 00:13:01.989
in Torrevieja, the same Spanish town Zykov had identified. It looks like

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:15.989
Zykov was right. Putin got a house in Spain. So in St Petersburg, Putin

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:19.989
learned how to profit from power. He also built a loyal team. After he

00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:26.989
moved to the Kremlin, they came with him. The men closest to Putin have

00:13:27.000 --> 00:13:30.989
been with him for years. They were with him here in St Petersburg and

00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:35.989
they've stayed with him ever since. This is the group that he trusts and

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:43.989
that he rewards, and this is the group that runs Russia. Putin's

00:13:44.000 --> 00:13:49.989
lawyer at the Town Hall became president and then Prime Minister of

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:57.989
Russia. His former deputy also served as prime minister. The Chief

00:13:58.000 --> 00:14:02.989
of Staff at the Town Hall now runs Russia's anti-drugs agency. His

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:13.989
former assistant now runs the biggest oil company in the world.

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:16.989
And his form ere economist -- former economist now runs the biggest gas

00:14:17.000 --> 00:14:23.989
company in the world. All of them worked with Putin in this building.

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:31.989
They rose up together. They went with him to Moscow. They have been a

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:37.989
very stable elite. This whole group, who grabbed the commanding heights

00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:39.989
of the Russian economy, they all work together in a very small

00:14:40.000 --> 00:14:51.989
office, in fact, in St Petersburg. As President, Putin was at the

00:14:52.000 --> 00:15:00.989
centre of this new elite. He had power and access to the super-rich.

