was one of the unwitting donors to Putin's Palace. He thought all his

00:15:16.000 --> 00:15:25.989
cash would be spent on health care, and he gave more than $200 million.

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:34.989
TRANSLATION: Abramovich's role was rather simple. He provided $203

