as good for anyone other than Vladimir Putin. A 35mm or is yacht

00:16:36.000 --> 00:16:44.989
like this one. -- 35 Ian dollars yacht. Given by Roman Abramovich.

00:16:45.000 --> 00:16:49.989
And our source is the man who managed the yacht.

