Putin about corruption. Khordorkovsky was jailed for tax

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:05.989
evasion and embezzlement. His business was taken by the Russian

00:19:06.000 --> 00:19:09.989
state. The beauty of the system is that it's organise and run according

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:13.989
to the old adage, for my friends everything, for my enemies the law.

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:19.989
The message that Putin chose to send to all of them was, I can put you in

00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:30.989
prison for anything. I don't need to have a watertight case. That is the

