anything. We don't know who is telling the truth about Pugachev's

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:28.989
fortune, but the allegation is clear, Putin controls the super-rich

00:20:29.000 --> 00:20:33.989
in Russia. People who possess a fortune, a large business in Russia,

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:37.989
realise that they do not own this, because everything depends on Putin.

00:20:38.000 --> 00:20:46.989
