seen him enriching his friends, his close allies. And marginalising

00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:36.989
those who he doesn't view as friends. Using state assets. Whether

00:21:37.000 --> 00:21:39.989
that is Russia's energy wealth, whether it is other state contracts,

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:43.989
he directs those to whom he believes will serve him and excludes those

00:21:44.000 --> 00:21:54.989
who don't. And if you want to make money in

00:21:55.000 --> 00:21:59.989
Russia, this is the industry, the nation's greatest riches are in oil

00:22:00.000 --> 00:22:05.989
and gas. Russia exports well over 1 billion barrels of oil per year. And

