Putin came and established a system where high rank officials want to

00:22:17.000 --> 00:22:21.989
control vital strategic assets. What we have now is a bunch of shady guys

00:22:22.000 --> 00:22:25.989
who barely appear in public, who control vital businesses linked to

00:22:26.000 --> 00:22:31.989
the state, which makes one wonder whether they are real beneficiaries

00:22:32.000 --> 00:22:43.989
or somebody superpowerful is behind their back.

